---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy · Exclusive Mentorship">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed muted">
      <p>We collect only what's needed to verify your payment and deliver access: your order details, the payment screenshot you share with us, and your Telegram identifier. We do not sell your data.</p>
      <p>There is no account or password on this site. Payment is sent directly to our crypto wallets or exchange UIDs and verified manually from the screenshot you share with us — we never see or store your exchange login or card details.</p>
      <p>Access delivery and all support happen via Telegram. Your Telegram identifier may be used to grant or revoke access based on your purchase.</p>
      <p>You may request deletion of your data at any time via Telegram support.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
